    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly indistinguishable from a brand-new model. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, factory-fresh luster without a single chip or swirl mark, while the interior remains pristine with the original 'new car' scent and no signs of wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment with all service records up to date. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a showroom-quality vehicle that drives exactly as it did on day one.",
