    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to own. It\u2019s in wonderful shape and has been super well-cared for over the years. It drives like a charm and is perfect for anyone looking for a solid, dependable car that still looks great on the road. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014come check it out and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit maintains its high-revving character with crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's known weak points. While showing honest signs of road use consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity remains high, providing a visceral, analog driving experience that modern coupes fail to replicate.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and long-term reliability. This car has been a dependable companion, and its current state reflects a history of consistent care. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals the expected minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful road use. All original body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels remain in excellent shape with plenty of tread left on the tires. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is free from tears or heavy stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free. Every button, switch, and electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound. It starts eagerly, idles smoothly, and shifts through all gears without hesitation. We have kept up with all scheduled fluid changes and filter replacements, ensuring it is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence. Included are two sets of keys and a complete folder of service receipts. This is a solid, honest car for someone who appreciates quality and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated to meet rigorous standards of performance and aesthetic presentation. It offers a seamless integration of reliability and sophisticated engineering, ensuring a superior experience for the discerning driver. Thoroughly inspected and maintained to preserve its structural and mechanical integrity, this offering represents an exceptional acquisition for those seeking enduring value and professional-grade quality.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
