      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS bulletproofing, ensuring the structural and mechanical longevity of the chassis. The suspension remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, offering the precise turn-in and lateral stability expected of the M-chassis. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains robust and optimized for performance driving.",
